RESEARCH ALERT - Hogy Medical cut . Daiwa Institute of Research Ltd downgraded Hogy Medical Co Ltd to a " B " rating from its previous " A " , Daiwa Securities brokers said on Tuesday . In its three - grade rating system , the research institute assigns a " B " rating to issues whose values it sees moving within 10 percentage points in either direction of the Tokyo Stock Exchange first - section TOPIX index over the next six months . 
